name: Corsair A330-343 [F-HZEN] Taxi and Takeoff from Montréal-Trudeau ᴴᴰ
description:
Another new airline for me! Here we have a regular flight from Corsair International, a French leisure airline that primarily flies out of Paris Orly Airport. Here we have one of 2 A330-300s currently in their fleet taxiing and taking off from runway 24R, with ATC included (from LiveATC.net). Enjoy!

Shoutout to CYUL Plane Spotter for showing me around that day. Check out his channel here: http://www.youtube.com/CYULPlaneSpotter

Thanks for watching!
